title: Born in '86 with DJ Demers
description:
Joe is joined by the amazing DJ Demers from America's Got Talent and The Conan O'brien Show. They chat about interpreters at comedy shows before getting into some absolutely hilarious teacher emails which include the cutest poop story you've ever heard!
